    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the Double VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure optimal torsional rigidity. The suspension remains tight, utilizing factory-spec bushings and dampers for signature M-division feedback. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the exterior retains a deep, factory-fresh luster with zero paint correction required. A truly visceral driving machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
